# Admin live data

Data-heavy admin pages use **client cache boot + background revalidation**, not TanStack Query.

## Canonical pattern (all data pages)

Every list/dashboard page follows the same three layers:

| Layer | File | Responsibility |
|---|---|---|
| `page.tsx` | route | `setRequestLocale` only → `*PageShell` from `admin-data-page-shells.tsx` |
| `AdminCachedPageShell` | `admin-cached-page-shell.tsx` | `useAdminCachedBoot` → warm cache paints instantly; cold → layout `*Skeleton` + prefetch |
| `*Dashboard` | feature folder | `useAdminLiveData` for refresh/revalidate; receives `initialData` from shell |

Wire new pages in **`admin-data-page-shells.tsx`** only — do not add per-page boot logic.

## Infrastructure

1. **`useAdminCachedBoot`** — `useSyncExternalStore` over `subscribeAdminCache`; SSR snapshot empty, client reads warm cache before paint. Kicks `prefetch` in `useLayoutEffect` on cold load.
2. **`client-data-cache.ts`** — typed `read/write/prefetch` per resource; `dedupedPrefetch` for inflight dedup; `clearAdminCacheForOrg` on event switch.
3. **`AdminStaffProvider`** (layout) — role + active event name; shells use `useAdminCan` for permission-gated chrome. No per-page `requireOrgPageContext` on data routes.
4. **`useAdminLiveData`** — seeds from shell `initialData` + cache; `suspenseBound: true` (default) skips pathname revalidate; 10s deferred silent refresh when data already painted.
5. **Sidebar** — prefetch all resources on mount + nav hover.

## Skeleton contract

- **Cold load only:** full-page `*Skeleton` (chrome + content layout) via `AdminCachedPageShell`
- **Never:** `AdminSuspenseFallback` pulse on data pages (removed); never stack route `loading.tsx` under `[org_slug]/`
- **Dashboards:** no inner content-skeleton branches — boot layer owns first paint

## Adding a new data page

1. Add `read/write/prefetch` in `client-data-cache.ts`
2. Add `*Skeleton` + `*Dashboard` in feature folder
3. Add `FooPageShell` in `admin-data-page-shells.tsx`
4. `page.tsx`: locale + `<FooPageShell orgSlug locale />`
5. Register prefetch in `admin-sidebar.tsx` `prefetchForNavKey`

## Exceptions

- **Settings, event detail, forms** — inline SSR or local state; no cache boot until they become list-heavy.
- **Placeholder pages** — static `PageShell` empty states.

## Never

- Per-page `useState(() => readCache())` — hydration ignores client cache
- SSR `*PageData` + Suspense for list pages — blocks navigation on slow queries
- Duplicate auth in `page.tsx` — layout + `AdminStaffProvider` handle staff gate
- `showContentSkeleton` in dashboards — cold load is shell responsibility
- Clear only dashboard cache on event switch — use `clearAdminCacheForOrg`
